    "english": "O Allah, on this day, (please) decide my fasting to be as same as the fasting of the true fasters, decide my acts of worship to be as same as the worship of the worshippers, awaken me from the slumber of the inadvertent ones, excuse my offense on this day, O God of the worlds, and pardon me, O He Who pardons the offenders!"
